snippet.title: Gunboat God - Official Developer Overview Trailer | The MIX | Kinda Funny Spring Showcase 2025
snippet.description: Get a deep dive into the gameplay of Gunboat God in this trailer for the upcoming shoot 'em up action game. Learn about upgrades, abilities and more as a developer from Janson RAD gives a breakdown about what you can expect from Gunboat God ahead of its launch on PC. Become the all-powerful Gunboat God. Carve the waves as you stylishly fight hordes of monsters in hundreds of quick-fire missions. Transform your Gunboat and upgrade your weapons, skills and abilities to take on giant, challenging, multi-stage bosses!
